a8%b4%2c1806%2c20200212%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TPHM,108,上訴,1806,20200212,1","JYEAR":"108","JCASE":"上訴","JNO":"1806","JDATE":"20200212","JTITLE":"偽造文書"}